{"tid":884270,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得自己肥既入","createTime":"2018-10-31T12:45:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-01T00:12:34.000Z","uid":65312,"like":14,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d940c85efef7acd409a478e4f70d4aa0ec123d08","tid":884270,"uid":65312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T12:45:20.000Z","msg":"是咁的, 今日食lunch間餐廳太多人要搭枱<br />\n經理安排我同同事坐左係兩隻地獄級暴肥西對面<br />\n其實已經即時冇晒胃口, 唔通唔食咩？<br />\n<br />\n食咩唔係重點<br />\n食左乾炒牛河走洋蔥<br />\n炒功到家, 碟底油不多<br />\n牛肉大片完整, 厚身, 食落有牛味<br />\n茶棕色醬油均勻, 河粉透薄分明, 乾身煙韌<br />\n<br />\n突然聽到暴肥西1講: <br />\n    我今日好健康呀, 食左好多菜(白菜仔一條)<br />\n然後連續食左三塊大雞扒, 再同暴肥西2講<br />\n    今日減肥成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n暴肥西2:<br />\n    我今朝食左好多菜, 所以今餐要食多少少似均衡返<br />\n之後一口氣食左7舊豬頸肉<br />\n<br />\n肥真係有原因, 死肥西好心照下塊鏡啦<br />\n豬到咁仲係到討論邊個邊個追你, 盲既都聽到你地講大話啦.<br />\n<br />\n埋單仲要撞到我隻手, 即時油到我成對筷子都跌埋<br />\n仲想開口話我非禮佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好彩我靈機一觸, 即時塞左條野落佢個口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後想問, 對筷子應該整跌個個執定用緊個個執？"},{"pid":"8f582cf39f17cc6f6b8fe0d885318a311d02fca8","tid":884270,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T12:49:00.000Z","msg":"Sor lo <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e90be61fdc9f42d82388d242f62f199117cb5d2c","tid":884270,"uid":1870,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T13:15:23.000Z","msg":"你自己睇返段野會唔會覺得好老尷？"},{"pid":"626d1b0e9b64b39e4ab01fac69a5d3ec1702e434","tid":884270,"uid":67462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T13:59:24.000Z","msg":"嗰條野咩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f727f7e0a23064c37fc550baaacc101ea96e037e","tid":884270,"uid":7071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T15:30:32.000Z","msg":"識食一定係用翻肥妹仔用過的筷子黎食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"449bbcb958ce63be2daf3f9ffaa0c1b15b163a02","tid":884270,"uid":123053,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T16:22:36.000Z","msg":"對肥婆嚟講1條菜係多喎<br />\n7舊肉算少啦 唔係都唔會咁肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff75ac1ae37e1966cde7ac6ad4bb50c69ee91861","tid":884270,"uid":219543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T16:35:28.000Z","msg":"6/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bd55ce5b062fa1c0d6630964957a650b50c146b","tid":884270,"uid":147195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T17:00:21.000Z","msg":"即時塞左條野落佢個口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 勇者"},{"pid":"51aa4dc7945359a8fe59a7dc83e58358c067e279","tid":884270,"uid":65312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"626d1b0e9b64b39e4ab01fac69a5d3ec1702e434","tid":884270,"uid":67462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T13:59:24.000Z","msg":"嗰條野咩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T00:03:26.000Z","msg":"雄風<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ec6d9ce33e9f3b67daba538ba32e5931b4e04ac","tid":884270,"uid":203714,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T00:05:09.000Z","msg":"好撚低質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁都有人正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a4dbec3d630b6241d38783523556c99e20d89e5","tid":884270,"uid":114976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T00:09:25.000Z","msg":"下半唔掂"},{"pid":"5d17c3d97702796d74de488234ffaeb3409e6552","tid":884270,"uid":140167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r